votebox.events

Class VoteBoxEventNotifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • votebox.events.VoteBoxEventNotifier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VoteBoxEventListener

    public class VoteBoxEventNotifier
extends java.lang.Object
implements VoteBoxEventListener
    The VoteBoxEventNotifier can be treated as a VoteBoxEventListener, as it implements all of the methods. However it differs in that it contains an array of listeners, and forwards events received onto those listeners (in the order they were registered).
